videos.description: McKenzie Milton hooks up with Gabriel Davis for a 30-yard catch to set up a touchdown for Central Florida.
videos.headline: Central Florida's Davis makes leaping catch

videos.description: Otis Anderson runs to the outside for a 3-yard touchdown to give Central Florida the lead early in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Central Florida's Anderson runs to the end zone untouched

videos.description: Adrian Killins Jr. runs up the middle for a 4-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Central Florida's Killins runs up the gut for TD run

videos.description: McKenzie Milton finds Marlon Williams on a screen pass for a 6-yard touchdown, to give Williams his first touchdown of the season.
videos.headline: Central Florida scores third first-quarter TD of game

videos.description: David Pindell throws to a wide open Mason Donaldson in the end zone for a 12-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Connecticut closes gap with TD catch

videos.description: McKenzie Milton throws a strike to Tre'Quan Smith over the middle on 2nd & 20 for a 41-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Central Florida's Smith scores 41-yard TD

videos.description: Mike Hughes beats his man in one-on-one coverage and picks off an overthrown ball by David Pindell.
videos.headline: Central Florida grabs game's first takeaway

videos.description: David Pindell floats a pass over the middle to Arkeel Newsome for a 60-yard catch.
videos.headline: Connecticut gets into red zone with 60-yard reception

videos.description: David Pindell runs to the end zone for 9 yards to trim Central Florida's lead to 28-17.
videos.headline: Connecticut closes the gap with TD run

videos.description: Otis Anderson breaks free for a 34-yard catch and run, but Tre Bell comes from behind to strip the ball loose as Connecticut recovers.
videos.headline: Connecticut catches a break with forced fumble

videos.description: McKenzie Milton connects with Tre'Quan Smith for a 39-yard catch at Connecticut's 14-yard line.
videos.headline: Central Florida' Smith hangs on for 39-yard pick up

videos.description: McKenzie Milton runs up the middle for a 4-yard touchdown to widen Central Florida's lead to 42-17 in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Central Florida's Milton runs in TD

videos.description: Noah Vedral delivers a pass to a wide open Cam Stewart for a 35-yard touchdown on his first pass of the game.
videos.headline: Central Florida's backup QB throws TD on first throw

videos.description: Despite the 49-24 win, Central Florida's head coach Scott Frost says his team made a lot of mistakes and needs to play better moving forward.
videos.headline: Frost: Central Florida didn't play best game

videos.description: Otis Anderson runs for 84 yards and two touchdowns to help UCF remain undefeated with a 49-24 victory over Connecticut.
videos.headline: UCF drops Connecticut to improve to 9-0
